title.rendered: Alticor Inc’ MLPOE Project Receives Two More Awards

content.rendered:
Alticor Inc’ Mariposa Land Port of Entry project in Nogales, Arizona, was recently awarded another two exciting project awards, both from Engineering News Record (ENR):

• ENR Southwest Project of the Year Award, Transportation + Aviation Category, 2015
• ENR Global Merit Award, Transportation + Aviation Category, 2015

This incredibly successful project now has received a total of 11 project awards!
